name: StoeyP,"We become one"
description: The NFT collaboration of two Thai NFT artists, "StoeyP and RBNeallaen". Both of us love to take a photograph since we were young, and we also love to make an artwork in our own styles. This project then is totally fulfill our passion and we would like to make it as one of prototypes for everyone who want to have an amazing NFT collaboration like we did. We hope our arts can make you feel joy, warm, love and happy. Thank you, love!
